A checklist of things you need to do in the proposal

----------------------
INSTITUTIONAL PI STUFF
----------------------

1) Add your institution to institutions.config

2) Add your personnel to personnel.config

3) Add your cover page to proposal/covers/ (see README therein).

4) Add your facilities description to proposals/facilities/ (see
   README therein).

--------------------------
ALL PARTICIPANTS - GENERAL
--------------------------

5) Look at the abstract in the formatted PDF and confirm that your
   name is presented as you prefer.  If not, edit
   proposal/personnel.config.

6) Add your biographical sketch to proposal/bios/ (see README therein).

7) Add your current & pending support to proposal/other-support/ (see
   README therein).
